        <p>The boundary of the GPS co-ordinates, displayed as a radius in metres. The Get Location feature on the TN14 App is used to automatically set GPS co-ordinates. The Accuracy (radius) refines as the GPS co-ordinates comes within range. This is indicated when the Accuracy value changes from red to green.</p>
